----------------
  libcam1394-0.1.2(beta)
----------------
add
 - support OpenCV's IPL compat libraries. CopyIplImage(IplImage*) can
   copy image to IplImage structure directly.
 - add document in doc directory. These docments are generatedi
   by Doxygen.   
fix
 - code clean up
 - fix some incorrect include path.
 - Under some distribution like RedHat Linux 7.2, the libtool 
   scripts may illegal shared library. 
